{"id": "28622", "post": "<div class=\"post-28622 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-bunny tag-bunny-net tag-cdn\" id=\"post-28622\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/bunny-net-says-expiring-credits-are-not-our-thing/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Bunny.net Says Expiring Credits Are \u201cNot Our Thing\u201d</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/bunny/\" rel=\"tag\">bunny</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/bunny-net/\" rel=\"tag\">bunny.net</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/cdn/\" rel=\"tag\">cdn</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> November 10, 2021 @ 5:58 pm, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bunny2.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-25035 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bunny2.png.webp\" alt=\"Bunny.net\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" align=\"right\" hspace=\"20\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bunny2.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bunny2-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bunny2.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/bunny2-150x150.png.webp 150w\" data-was-processed=\"true\">Community favorite CDN bunny.net recently sent an email to customers informing them that they are doing away with expiring credits.&nbsp; Combined with their lack of monthly minimums, this makes bunny.net a truly awesome CDN to partner with.</p><p>According to <a href=\"https://lowendtalk.com/discussion/175036/bunny-net-removes-the-top-up-criteria-and-account-credit-is-for-lifetime-now\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"LowEndTalk\">their email</a>:</p><p><em>\u201cAt bunny.net, it\u2019s our goal to become the most customer centric company in the industry. As part of that, we decided expiring credits are absolutely not our thing.</em></p><p><em>We are delighted to announce that effective immediately, all grandfathered accounts such as yours that still operate on our old billing system will no longer have their credits expire while still keeping the benefit of not having any monthly minimums.</em></p><p><em>This means you can enjoy your account balance for the life of your account with no additional payments required as long as you maintain a positive balance.</em></p><p><em>Thank you for making the internet hop faster! \ud83d\ude80\u201d</em></p><p>You might enjoy reading our <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/interview-qa-with-dejan-from-bunnycdn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"interview\">interview the the head bunny</a>, Dejan.</p><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-container\"><h3>Related posts:</h3><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-container\"><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/outage-at-akamai-takes-down-major-internet-sites/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"Akamai Outage Takes Internet Down\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/site-down-2-150x150.jpg) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single